            "summary": "Unsafe Java deserialization in Apache MINA's ObjectSerializationDecoder allows remote unauthenticated attackers to achieve RCE by sending crafted serialized data. Affects MINA core 2.0.x, 2.1.x, and 2.2.x. Patched versions (2.0.27, 2.1.10, 2.2.4) require additional class allowlist configuration to be effective.",
